SOQLResult.name: SOQLResult
SOQLResult.description: A complex type that represents the result of a SOQL query in an ApexExecutionOverlayResult object.

queryMetadata.description: QueryResultMetadata includes the following fields: columnMetadata entityName groupBy idSelected keyPrefix

queryResult.description: MapValue contains an array of MapEntry, which contains the following fields: keyDisplayValue value (reference to StateValue)
